    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 2001 Honda S2000, a definitive AP1 variant in showroom state. Powered by the high-compression F20C inline-four, this unit exhibits perfect VTEC crossover and maintains factory-spec valve clearances. The longitudinal drivetrain is anchored by a precise close-ratio six-speed manual and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The double-wishbone suspension remains taut, with all bushings and dampers showing no signs of fatigue or degradation. Featuring original VIN-matched panels and a pristine undercarriage, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
